        "TileImage": "$($repository fb3b5baf-8e2d-4e22-aeba-78651e628842).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome back to Sapienza, or should I say Echoes of Sapienza. The town of Sapienza&apos;s security has been found to be lacking, along with this disease and other assassinations. That&apos;s why I don&apos;t want any bodies found unless it&apos;s an accident or poisoning. Tonight&apos;s target is Salvatore Bravuomo. We don&apos;t have much information about Salvatore. The client told me that he is a financier, buying influence and destroying competitors. You must also assassinate his bodyguard just in case. Have fun!",
